1. topics list
kafka-topics --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

2. Create topic
kafka-topics --create --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1 --topic raw-weather --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

3. Describe topic
kafka-topics --describe --topic raw-weather --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

4. Read topic
kafka-console-consumer --topic raw-weather --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092